{"tid":1159132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"龍緯汶：我與小四大哥哥的情義","createTime":"2019-05-17T12:28:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T13:19:07.000Z","uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"db66cd4b4f40b5d86f1f16898530cd11bd35a6f4","tid":1159132,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T12:28:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1057186\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1057186&d=LRk9npnliL4HefRMP%2BWOkBphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=4a05cffa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1057186&h=b7d6d76c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1057186</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/files/styles/w775/public/column_images/melung.jpeg?itok=1vt5BnSE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fw775%2Fpublic%2Fcolumn_images%2Fmelung.jpeg%3Fitok%3D1vt5BnSE&h=5134f1fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n文：龍緯汶（油尖旺食物銀行行長）（鳴謝投稿）<br />\n<br />\n2016年1月，朋友轉介了一個印尼家庭給油尖旺食物銀行。他們一家五口、爸爸是一位宣教士，靠著奉獻過活，生活自然困苦。加上家中天花及牆身滲水，一家都非常煩惱。<br />\n<br />\n食物銀行到他們家中探訪，打開假天花一看，竟然有一個可以望到天空的洞！食物銀行協助他們搬到一個新的居所，他們亦定期到食物銀行領取食物。<br />\n<br />\n印尼家庭的三個小朋友，也常協助食物銀行做義工。有一次，讀小四的大哥哥問我：「Uncle James，我可不可以把這些文具送給同學們，與他們一起分享？」我回答說：「當然可以！」<br />\n<br />\n有一次，他們的父母有些事情要做，我協助到學校接三個小朋友放學。大哥哥介紹他的同學們給我認識：「這就是 Uncle James，送文具給我們的那一位...」<br />\n<br />\n於是，我乘機跟同學們及他們的家長介紹一下食物銀行的理念。<br />\n<br />\n如果你問，小四的大哥哥是食物銀行的什麼人？我會答：他是我們的朋友、義工及宣傳大使！"},{"pid":"54073eaf5509056abe5120e4523ce63844e704a3","tid":1159132,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T12:30:23.000Z","msg":"佢真人有無160<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24b04017eaf283813966fc5e6a91f064374e6b12","tid":1159132,"uid":54303,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"54073eaf5509056abe5120e4523ce63844e704a3","tid":1159132,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T12:30:23.000Z","msg":"佢真人有無160<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T12:32:09.000Z","msg":"一定無 <br />\n米四差唔多"},{"pid":"5ae038818fac06542219d9dc22edb2852e54c09f","tid":1159132,"uid":29080,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T12:32:28.000Z","msg":"同小四一樣高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d9325204f0ccfe949d5d2ac4acc8499dad0b7a4","tid":1159132,"uid":20609,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"24b04017eaf283813966fc5e6a91f064374e6b12","tid":1159132,"uid":54303,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"54073eaf5509056abe5120e4523ce63844e704a3","tid":1159132,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T12:30:23.000Z","msg":"佢真人有無160<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T12:32:09.000Z","msg":"一定無 <br />\n米四差唔多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T12:33:36.000Z","msg":"我以為佢屈低身同個小朋友影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f3a1a1aaa8b7d3de1742738321efd3cec2c9fb","tid":1159132,"uid":49456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5ae038818fac06542219d9dc22edb2852e54c09f","tid":1159132,"uid":29080,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T12:32:28.000Z","msg":"同小四一樣高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T12:34:08.000Z","msg":"係矮過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14912d5d14fe62e39f510e49635495eb7fbd8b6a","tid":1159132,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T12:34:29.000Z","msg":"分分中69超過20cm又話你知咩"},{"pid":"5b6842653a613dc9f04a563f4fd980135dfd4a3f","